The use of tensors in the proposed framework suggests that the paper may also be relevant to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The practical applications mentioned in the abstract, such as retail-planning and forecasting, suggest that the paper may also be relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
